'''Christoph Zuercher''' is Professor at the Graduate School of Public and International Affairs at the [[University of Ottawa]], where he has been since 2008. He used to be a professor of [[Political science|Political Science]] at the [[Free University of Berlin|Free University]] in Berlin. He was also a Humboldt fellow at the Center on Democracy, Development and the Role of Law at [[Stanford University]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Christoph Zuercher, PhD |url=http://fsi.stanford.edu/people/christophzuercher/|work=Freeman Spogli Institute for International Studies|publisher=Stanford University|accessdate=16 January 2011}}</ref>

